Description: AD-PKI Debian Installer
 AD-PKI installs the base files for the AD-PKI system.
 .
 The package provides configuration templates, systemd unit files,
 installer scripts, filesystem layout preparation and command line tools.
 .
 Runtime components such as PHP, Nginx, Apache2, PostgreSQL, Node.js
 and Go are installed later through the interactive adpki-install command.